<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Amar Kotha</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">

    <link rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

    <div class="hero">

        <h1>
            💬 Amar Kotha
        </h1>

        <p>
            An elegant light-themed platform to share your thoughts, read what others say, and make your voice heard.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-buttons">

            <a href="/comments" class="btn primary">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-comments"></i>
                Read Entries
            </a>

            <a href="/comments/new" class="btn success">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                Add Entry
            </a>

        </div>

    </div>

    <h2 class="features-title">
        ✨ The Canvas of Expression
    </h2>

    <div class="features-grid">

        <div class="feature-card">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-pen-nib"></i>
            <h3>Share Your Story</h3>
            <p>Pour your emotions, stories, and daily expressions into words instantly on a beautiful canvas.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i>
            <h3>Connect & React</h3>
            <p>Express alignment or feelings by liking or disliking entries that speak to your heart.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-feather"></i>
            <h3>Minimal & Light</h3>
            <p>A distraction-free, light-mode interface crafted specifically for absolute reading pleasure.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i>
            <h3>Always Preserved</h3>
            <p>Backed by MongoDB database structure to keep your memories and thoughts safe forever.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>